## Part C — OTA Concurrency & Overbooking (from Audit #12)

> [!CAUTION]
> **Highest-risk gap**: No protection against OTA+Website race condition:
> 1. Guest A books on Booking.com at 14:00
> 2. RPA syncs at 14:05 (next cycle)
> 3. Guest B books on website at 14:03 (before sync)
> 4. Both succeed → **overbooking**

**Fix**: Add overbooking detection cron in `booking-cron` (already exists).

